@@TJvCustomRollOut.GroupIndex
Summary
  Index of the group this rollout belongs to.
Description
  GroupIndex holds the index of the group this rollout is part of. If several rollouts have a
  GroupIndex > 0, they will behave as a radio group: when one rollout is expanded, the others are
  collapsed. To disable the radio group behavior, set GroupIndex to 0.

